body:
Concatenated constant zeros in input A can be removed.
In this special case, after removing constant, input width be then 1, when the cell could be changed to $not, which might enable further optimisation.

```
       "_10298_": {
          "hide_name": 1,
          "type": "$logic_not",
          "parameters": {
            "A_SIGNED": 0,
            "A_WIDTH": 2,
            "Y_WIDTH": 1
          },
          "port_directions": {
            "A": "input",
            "Y": "output"
          },
          "connections": {
            "A" : [["_02009_", 0], [0]],
            "Y" : ["_03931_"]
          }
        },
```
